<h1>远</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">yuǎn</span><span class=alesi>(yuan3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 远 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 远</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/distant" style="color:black;">distant</a>, <a href="/dictionary/remote" style="color:black;">remote</a>, <a href="/dictionary/far" style="color:black;">far</a>; profound</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 7<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 7 strokes: <a href="/character/我" title="wo3: our, us, i, me, my, we">我</a>, <a href="/character/这" title="zhe4: this, the, here">这</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a>, <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/作" title="zuo4: make; work; compose, write; act, perform">作</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/没" title="mei2: not, have not, none; drown, sink">没</a>, <a href="/character/还" title="hai2: still, yet, also, besides">还</a>, <a href="/character/进" title="jin4: advance, make progress, enter">进</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/辵" title="Kangxi radical 162">辵</a>&nbsp;162.4</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 2 <br><small>Other HSK 2 characters: <a href="/character/始" title="shi3: begin, start; then, only then">始</a>, <a href="/character/准" title="zhun3: approve, allow, permit; in accord">准</a>, <a href="/character/夫" title="fu1: man, male adult, husband; those">夫</a>, <a href="/character/备" title="bei4: prepare, ready, perfect">备</a>, <a href="/character/近" title="jin4: near, close; approach; intimate">近</a>, <a href="/character/往" title="wang3: go, depart; past, formerly">往</a>, <a href="/character/快" title="kuai4: rapid, quick, speedy, fast; soon">快</a>, <a href="/character/百" title="bai3: one hundred; numerous, many">百</a>, <a href="/character/每" title="mei3: every, each">每</a>, <a href="/character/离" title="li2: rare beast; strange; elegant">离</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-2" title="List of HSK 2 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 2 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 386</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 0608</p><p><b>Traditional variant:</b> <a href="/character/遠">遠</a></p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/中远" title="Zhong1 yuan3">中远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/久远" title="jiu3 yuan3">久远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/偏远" title="pian1 yuan3">偏远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/僻远" title="pi4 yuan3">僻远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/威远" title="Wei1 yuan3">威远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/安远" title="An1 yuan3">安远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/定远" title="Ding4 yuan3">定远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/宁远" title="Ning2 yuan3">宁远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/差远" title="cha4 yuan3">差远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/平远" title="Ping2 yuan3">平远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/悠远" title="you1 yuan3">悠远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/怀远" title="Huai2 yuan3">怀远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/扯远" title="che3 yuan3">扯远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/招远" title="Zhao1 yuan3">招远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/抚远" title="Fu3 yuan3">抚远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/最远" title="zui4 yuan3">最远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/永远" title="yong3 yuan3">永远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/深远" title="shen1 yuan3">深远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/渊远" title="yuan1 yuan3">渊远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/清远" title="Qing1 yuan3">清远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/渺远" title="miao3 yuan3">渺远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/玄远" title="xuan2 yuan3">玄远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/甩远" title="shuai3 yuan3">甩远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/疏远" title="shu1 yuan3">疏远</a>, <a href="/dictionary/绥远" title="Sui2 yuan3">绥远</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">遠|远[<span style="color:#009900;">yuǎn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- far<br>- distant<br>- remote<br>- (intensifier in a comparison) by far<br>- much (lower etc)<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">遠|远[<span style="color:#000099;">yuàn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to distance oneself from (classical)<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+8FDC</p></div>

